00:45:18.296 --> 00:45:21.010 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: I'm, once again,
going to tell you a story.

00:45:21.010 --> 00:45:27.376 align:middle line:84%
Choices, just imagine walking
down the street, New York City.

00:45:27.376 --> 00:45:31.440 align:middle line:84%
Those of you who have visited
New York, the Big Apple.

00:45:31.440 --> 00:45:35.940 align:middle line:84%
The high-rise condos, boy,
these are million and a half,

00:45:35.940 --> 00:45:40.210 align:middle line:84%
$2 million condos before
