00:45:40.210 --> 00:45:43.432 align:middle line:84%
And I'm walking along, kind
of looking at the skyline.

00:45:43.432 --> 00:45:46.260 align:middle line:84%
And from a third story
balcony, flower pot

00:45:46.260 --> 00:45:49.940 align:middle line:90%
falls, bam, hits me in the head.

00:45:49.940 --> 00:45:54.840 align:middle line:84%
Falls to the ground, pot
breaks, flower falls out.

00:45:54.840 --> 00:45:55.700 align:middle line:90%
I have some choices.

00:45:55.700 --> 00:45:59.144 align:middle line:90%


00:45:59.144 --> 00:46:01.260 align:middle line:84%
I'll bet you can all
think of this one.

00:46:01.260 --> 00:46:04.020 align:middle line:84%
You sue this guy, he's
got a lot of bucks.

00:46:04.020 --> 00:46:06.070 align:middle line:90%
Look at the place he lives in.

00:46:06.070 --> 00:46:09.250 align:middle line:90%
And I'll claim concussion.

00:46:09.250 --> 00:46:12.335 align:middle line:84%
Get my digital little
portable phone out

00:46:12.335 --> 00:46:14.605 align:middle line:90%
and call my attorney right now.

00:46:14.605 --> 00:46:16.864 align:middle line:90%
You can do that.

00:46:16.864 --> 00:46:21.292 align:middle line:90%
