00:49:28.920 --> 00:49:33.840 align:middle line:84%
Should poor taxpayers be
forced to pay higher taxes

00:49:33.840 --> 00:49:36.320 align:middle line:84%
to put rich kids
into private schools?

00:49:36.320 --> 00:49:37.120 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wow.

00:49:37.120 --> 00:49:41.740 align:middle line:84%
>>TAYLOR: Now the question at
hand is about school vouchers.

00:49:41.740 --> 00:49:45.130 align:middle line:84%
If I happen to be a of
a very liberal bent,

00:49:45.130 --> 00:49:49.330 align:middle line:84%
