you know who, who

00:50:18.240 --> 00:50:21.410 align:middle line:84%
thinks the opposite
of what I think.

00:50:21.410 --> 00:50:21.910 align:middle line:90%
All right?

00:50:21.910 --> 00:50:22.470 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yep.

00:50:22.470 --> 00:50:24.650 align:middle line:90%
>>TAYLOR: That's the first part.

00:50:24.650 --> 00:50:29.260 align:middle line:84%
The second problem is,
this is a real issue.

00:50:29.260 --> 00:50:31.690 align:middle line:90%
We're adults, we all vote.

00:50:31.690 --> 00:50:36.760 align:middle line:84%
What on earth are we doing not
using our computers to Google,

00:50:36.760 --> 00:50:38.720 align:middle line:84%
or going to the
library and finding out

00:50:38.720 --> 00:50:40.260 align:middle line:90%
