00:50:41.930 --> 00:50:43.780 align:middle line:90%
Where does the money come from?

00:50:43.780 --> 00:50:46.970 align:middle line:84%
How does it impact
public education?

00:50:46.970 --> 00:50:48.400 align:middle line:90%
Da, da, da, da.

00:50:48.400 --> 00:50:53.140 align:middle line:84%
So instead of making
a conscious decision,

00:50:53.140 --> 00:50:57.390 align:middle line:84%
an intelligent decision, we're
in click-whirr mode, you know?

00:50:57.390 --> 00:50:58.765 align:middle line:84%
We think of the
mind as operating

00:50:58.765 --> 00:51:01.700 align:middle line:84%
