system two nowadays.

00:51:01.700 --> 00:51:04.190 align:middle line:84%
System one is the
automatic mode.

00:51:04.190 --> 00:51:06.520 align:middle line:90%
System one is fast.

00:51:06.520 --> 00:51:09.470 align:middle line:84%
System modes how 90%
of everything we do

00:51:09.470 --> 00:51:15.470 align:middle line:84%
